data.description: Elegant Tuscan-inspired residence nestled within the picturesque Las Brisas Del Rio community! This stunning 4-bedroom home offers the convenience of 2 full bathrooms and an expansive open living space complete with a cozy gas-log fireplace. The kitchen boasts custom tile countertops, crowned cabinetry, and two generous pantries, while the p suite features dual walk-in closets for added luxury. Enjoy the beauty of tile flooring throughout the living areas, kitchen, and all wet spaces. The utility room showcases rich hickory cabinets, and the front and back yards are thoughtfully landscaped to perfection. Refrigerated air. Additionally, a custom-built shed/workshop offers extra space for your creative endeavors.
